Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:50.38,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}你所萌生的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:53.39,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}定是正确无误之志
