Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:22:00.23,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.52,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.27,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:10.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:16.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:20.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:28.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:33.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:37.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.93,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:42.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:48.02,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:50.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}为我们指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:57.53,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}{\fad(0,800)}梦想必亲手实现
